lyrics:
[Verse]
In the depths of the night, shadows arise
Moonlight fades, as darkness mesmerizes
Lost in an abyss, where dreams go to die
Embracing the unknown, beneath the starlit sky

[Chorus]
Dancing with the darkness, feeling its caress
Synthwave rhythms, echoing distress
Glowing neon lights, contrasting the black
Swaying to the music, never looking back
